title: Talking RHONJ with Kim D
description:
New Jersey's fashion icon Kim D joins us to answer all our burning questions about RHONJ, Teresa, Melissa, Kim G, Danielle Staub, Posche Fashion show, and pretty much anything else that crosses our mind. Check it out!

Don't just listen to the interview, watch it! We recorded this over zoom; so come watch our threeway call with Kim D by clicking here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/42807919/

Our Patreon Extras: https://patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (Ben Mandelker & Ronnie Karam)
